            <title>[LU-14384] data &quot;written&quot; to last stripe of very large ldiskfs object can not be &quot;read&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14384</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ldiskfs max file size is 17592186040320 bytes, which 16777215 of full 1M and 1M without 4096 bytes.&lt;br/&gt;
